    "SDN can find optimal load assessment [12] and the optimal location for task processing [21], manage dynamic incoming traffic to network nodes, balance traffic load [22], and thus increase network efficiency and QoS [16].",
    "It is used to develop the IoT network as the SDN-based IoT network (SD-IoT) [16].",
    "In general, the IoT and SDN have a set of complementary requirements and capacities.",
    "IoT can strengthen SDN by solving the issues related to scalability, mobility, and real-time requirements.",
    "On the other hand, users have a series of QoS requirements that can be answered by combining the IoT and SDN.The IoT alone cannot solve the challenges related to the QoS."
